.container
  %div
    %h1.page-header See if you qualify in 3 simple steps
  .row
    %p.subhead.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2 Currently we provide social service programs for the city of Chicago and state of Illinois. Using mRelief, simplifies the qualifying process with an easy-to-use form that can be accessed online and through SMS.
  .row
    .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
      %h3 1. Choose Your Program
      %p From the horizontal menu, on the right-hand side, select “Programs”. From the dropdown menu, select “See All Programs”.  After landing on the Programs Page, choose the program that applies to your needs.
      .bluedivider
  .row
    .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
      %h3 2. Enter Your Information
      %p On the individual program page you selected, there will be a qualifier statement in the description followed by a few questions for you to fill out. In the form fields, provide your information.
      .bluedivider
  .row
    .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
      %h3 3. See if you Qualify
      %p After you have completed the form for your program, click the blue “See If I Qualify” button on the lower left-hand side.
  %br/
  .row
    .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2{:style => "text-align:center;"}
      %h4
        After you have completed this process, you will be directed to community or government resources based on your qualifying outcome.
        %br/
        %br/
        If you have any questions please contact us.
  %br/
  %br/
  %br/
